Single-database configuration for Flask.

Institut: agar "Can't locate revision identified by '...'" xatosi chiqsa
(bazadagi migratsiya versiyasi joriy migrations/versions da yo'q), bajarish:
  flask db-stamp-head
yoki avtomatik (avval upgrade, xato bo'lsa stamp head):
  flask db-fix-version
Keyin odatdagidek: flask db upgrade
